1 E. For purposes of this section, a private educational
2 institution as defined in paragraph (e) of Section 3102 of Title 70
3 of the Oklahoma Statutes, a private school defined as a nonpublic
4 entity conducting an educational program for at least one grade
5 between prekindergarten through twelve, a municipality as defined in
6 paragraph 5 of Section 1-102 of Title 11 of the Oklahoma Statutes or
7 a public trust with a municipality as its beneficiary may charge a
